          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1671544221110-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fill each <strong>warmed tortilla </strong>with the <strong>quick-pickled salad </strong>and <strong>sweet sesame Fable mushrooms</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>sriracha mayo </strong>and <strong>crispy breadcrumbs</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
